A proof of concept implementation for the Drupal site archive format.

Requires:
Drupal 6 (http://drupal.org), 
Backup and Migrate (http://drupal.org/project/backup_migrate)

To use:
Install Backup and Migrate and this module.
Go to admin/content/backup_migrate
Choose 'Site Archive' in the first pulldown on the 'Quick Backup' form.
Click 'Backup Now'.


For more information see: http://groups.drupal.org/node/106754